textBeforeTable: Portugal Head Coach Moncho Lopez: "First I want to thank Georgia's coach which is one more to recognize the quality of our game. Second, I want to say that Portugal is very well represented by these players: They are hard workers, inteligent and their atitude is unbelievable. Besides our limitations we played a good game." "Every game is important for us and ths was an important win. We had lot of pressure and we made errors that usualy we don't do. Congratulations to the portuguese coach because dispite of all the circunstancies and injuries they managed to play very well tonight and also Portugal was the team that played better against Belgium."
